This directory contains alternate queries for the TPCH benchmark.

### Polars derived queries
These queries were derived by translating polars plans back into SQL.
The source polars plans are found here 
https://github.com/pola-rs/polars-benchmark/tree/8975df5acb720c520dfdeb888d3668ba151f41df/queries/polars
The file queries_polars.json contains the translated queries.

### Best queries
This set contains all queries from the official TPCH benchmark except Q17 and Q21 which use the modified plan from queries_polars.json
The file queries_best.json contains the queries.
